3105
01:43:44,751 --> 01:43:45,752
Whether it's experimental methods

3106
01:43:45,752 --> 01:43:46,920
Or theoretical methods

3107
01:43:47,321 --> 01:43:50,290
So I think this might be

3108
01:43:50,290 --> 01:43:51,358
A good thing

3109
01:43:51,658 --> 01:43:55,062
But
I don't think this is unique to physics people either

3110
01:43:55,462 --> 01:43:57,931
Like
Why wouldn't computer science people have this trait

