Biology students also have this trait

3115
01:44:03,904 --> 01:44:05,839
So I don't think it's unique to physics

3116
01:44:06,273 --> 01:44:08,508
Right but actually it's quite interesting

3117
01:44:08,508 --> 01:44:10,577
There are indeed many in this field

3118
01:44:10,577 --> 01:44:13,080
